  <p>
    answers to some common questions about my work, experience, and interests.
  </p>
  
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h2>what technologies do you specialize in?</h2>
    <p>
      i primarily work with javascript and typescript, using frameworks like react and astro 
      for building web applications. i also have experience with python and rust, and i'm 
      always eager to learn new technologies that solve problems effectively.
    </p>
