      currently, i'm focused on my full-time position in software development. however, 
      i'm always open to discussing interesting projects or collaborations. feel free to 
      reach out via the contact page.
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h2>what's your development process like?</h2>
